'''Swoop analogs''' were the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]'s equivalent of the [[Swoop/Legends|swoop bikes]] used by the [[Galaxy/Legends|Galaxy]]. These open-air fliers could a seat a crew of two. Swoop analogs were equipped with a [[dovin basal]] propulsion unit which they used to drain the shields of enemy vehicles, overloading them and causing them to break down. They were also armed with [[Yaret-Kor|yaret-kors]].

==Appearances==
